@startgantt
' Global project schedule (sprint-level overview only).
' Task-level detail lives in the per-sprint Gantts: gantt-sprint1..4.puml.
skinparam backgroundColor transparent
skinparam defaultFontName Times New Roman
skinparam shadowing false
<style>
ganttDiagram {
  task {
    BackGroundColor #EAF2F8
    LineColor #004389
    FontColor #1A1A1A
  }
  milestone { BackGroundColor #004389 LineColor #003063 }
  note { BackGroundColor #FBF6DD LineColor #9A8C4A }
}
</style>
printscale weekly
Project starts 2026-02-02
saturday are closed
sunday are closed

[Sprint 0: Setup and Planning (1 week)] as [S0] lasts 5 days
[Sprint 1: Platform Foundation and UI (2 weeks)] as [S1] lasts 10 days
[S1] starts at [S0]'s end
[Sprint 2: Lead Capture and Duplicate Detection (2 weeks)] as [S2] lasts 10 days
[S2] starts at [S1]'s end
[Sprint 3: Analytics and Smart Follow-Up (2 weeks)] as [S3] lasts 10 days
[S3] starts at [S2]'s end
[Sprint 4: CRM Assistant and Live Integration (2 weeks)] as [S4] lasts 10 days
[S4] starts at [S3]'s end
[Testing, Deployment and Report (8 days)] as [TR] lasts 8 days
[TR] starts at [S4]'s end

[S0] is colored in #D6E4F0/#004389
[S1] is colored in #EAF2F8/#004389
[S2] is colored in #EAF2F8/#004389
[S3] is colored in #EAF2F8/#004389
[S4] is colored in #EAF2F8/#004389
[TR] is colored in #FBF6DD/#9A8C4A
@endgantt
